    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended only for those seeking a serious restoration project or a source for parts. The engine is currently non-operational and will require a full rebuild to be roadworthy again. Externally, the body exhibits significant rust, particularly around the wheel wells and undercarriage, and the paint has faded and peeled in several areas. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. Please note that this car will need to be towed from its current location. It is priced to reflect the substantial investment in time and resources required for repair.",
      "price": 3500.0,
