    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen that defines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained to a showroom-ready level, boasting a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and reliability. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of peerless quality and lasting value.",
      "price": 47900.0,
