      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule of automotive excellence. This isn't merely a vehicle; it is a preserved masterpiece that hums with the spirit of a golden era. Every line of its sculpted exterior catches the light with a mirror-like depth, while the interior welcomes you with the intoxicating scent of untouched leather and the silent promise of a sanctuary on wheels. To drive it is to command a symphony of precision engineering\u2014a smooth, effortless glide that makes the modern world melt away. It has been cherished not as a tool, but as a work of art, waiting for a connoisseur who understands that true character is timeless. Own a piece of history that feels as fresh as the day it first graced the open road.",
      "price": 44500.0,
